name: passion bug
description: @sianvictoriauk - Originally a photograph taken of a purple passion flower on the 1st August 2006. The image was mirrored and pixelated using old-school photosuite vista software that came with a Vivitar camera at the time. The creation was part of my 'Flashcore x photography'. A collection I made at age 15 but never shared. Today, 24/05/21 I've recovered it from a CD to finally get seen.
